  <h1 class="page-title">Home</h1>

  <p>Rust/Actix-web 4 implementation for the Rinha de Backend 2024/Q1 challenge. Manages a fictional bank API with transaction processing and balance statements under strict resource constraints (1.5 CPU, 550MB RAM total across all containers).</p>

