  <h2>Key Features</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Minimal single-file API implementation (~140 lines of Rust)</li>
    <li>Actix-web 4 with Tokio async runtime and SQLx 0.8</li>
    <li>PostgreSQL stored procedures for server-side business logic</li>
    <li>All requests under 800ms at 250MB RAM usage</li>
  </ul>

